#: data/effects/avfilter/avfilter_smartblur.xml:25
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Set the chroma radius.<br>\n"
"            The value specifies the variance of the gaussian filter used to blur the image (slower if larger). If not specified, it defaults to the value "
"set for <em>Luma radius</em>"
